- Define/extend endpoints in `[openapi.yaml](mdc:docs-cursor/api/openapi.yaml)` before implementing
- Use components for Error and Meta; standardize pagination (page/pageSize) and sorting
- Schemas must have explicit types/formats; reuse JSON Schemas in `[schemas](mdc:docs-cursor/api/schemas)`
